OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773335511
OL,3,CVan driver dies in crash on A27 near
OL,4,CChichester
OL,6,FA man has died following a collision
OL,7,Fon the A27 near Chichester.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,10,Feastbound carriageway at 5:30am on
OL,11,FWednesday (11 March) to reports of a
OL,12,Fcollision involving a silver Ford
OL,13,FTransit van.
OL,15,FThe driver of the van, a 53-year-old
OL,16,Fman died at the scene.
OL,18,FPolice say his next of kin have been
OL,19,Finformed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
