OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773335511
OL,3,CVan driver dies in crash on A27 near
OL,4,CChichester
OL,6,FThe road was closed from Warblington
OL,7,Fin the west to Fishbourne in the east
OL,8,Fbut has now reopened.
OL,10,FA Sussex Police spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"Officers have thanked motorists for
OL,12,Ftheir patience while we responded to
OL,13,Fthe collision.
OL,15,F"They are appealing for witnesses or
OL,16,Fanyone with information such as
OL,17,Fdashcam footage in the area at the
OL,18,Ftime to come forward.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
