OL,3,CVan driver dies in crash on A27 near
OL,4,CChichester
OL,6,F"The collision happened between
OL,7,Fsections over Newells Lane and Ratham
OL,8,FLane near Hambrook.
OL,10,F"Anyone with information can report it
OL,11,Fto Sussex Police online or email:
OL,12,Fcollision.appeal@sussex.police.uk and
OL,13,Fquote Operation Chilcote."
